    "updated_at": "2025-12-13T13:23:01Z",
    "body": "Can confirm.\nOn MacOS 26.2 (official release), Ghostty 1.2.3, omz master (f84341c), and Starship 1.24.1, \nSetting either `disabled = true` or `show_notifications = false` under `[cmd_duration]` solves the problem for me.",
